Ranger Help for: fortify
========================

SYNTAX:      fortify <direction>
USAGE:       forest,plains,swamp,desert,jungle,hills,road,beach,
             underground,mountain,arctic,barren
SLOT COST:   5
BASE SP:     30
SKILL TYPE:  defensive

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to gather materials from the surrounding
terrain and build a blockade or barricade in one direction, providing
defensive advantages. The blockade can be circumvented by trashing it,
allowing passage. How strong the blockade is and how much of a beating
it can take depends on how proficient the Ranger is at building them.
Other Rangers can pass through blockades freely, since they understand
the nature of such constructions.
